# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
* text=auto

# --- GitHub Linguist: keep generated/vendored files out of the language stats ---
# Linguist counts bytes, so large generated artifacts skew the language bar.
# In particular Gowin's place-&-route output uses the .p extension, which
# Linguist classifies as "Gnuplot" — exclude all per-board build output.
# (The previous patterns missed a2mega/a2p25/a2n20v2-GS and used the wrong
# a2n20v2_enhanced spelling, so those impl/ dirs were still being counted.)
boards/*/impl/**   linguist-generated
*.fs               linguist-generated
*.gprj             linguist-vendored
releases/**        linguist-vendored
